{"tid":1874850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔通我諗多左】睇完 廣東省立法徵用私人財產 嘅新聞⋯","createTime":"2020-02-11T12:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T17:20:05.000Z","uid":271554,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4bd126c383c327811d81dd3e1506f2de6de16e","tid":1874850,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:12:49.000Z","msg":"睇完個新聞<br />\n再睇下大家最近自發做嘢而政府好似死L左咁乜都唔做<br />\n再睇到有人想自做口罩生產線<br />\n再望返599章入面嘅8.3c 、8.4、8.6a、8.6b <br />\n<br />\n<strong>政府係咪等緊充公某啲嘢？</strong><br />\n<br />\n希望有人話俾我知只係我諗多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSOURCES：<blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap599%21zh-Hant-HK&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=8984de9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap599!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n599章《預防及控制疾病條例》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507925-20200211.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507925-20200211.htm&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=c80cd3f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507925-20200211.htm&h=0d94de10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507925-20200211.htm</a><br />\n廣東省緊急立法授權政府可徵用私人財產抗疫</blockquote>"},{"pid":"87e4ceb9b2a40bb68f65bee25f6ae1d5372bd2e4","tid":1874850,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"自推1次"},{"pid":"97daf8eb3f1ddb6dde4c7998349e956ae94473c8","tid":1874850,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"但係推唔郁"},{"pid":"b6f72dce5110dee8503b651066197124b5a44167","tid":1874850,"uid":271554,"like":0,"dislike":0,